---
// Hand icon (lucide)
---

<div class="flex flex-wrap sm:flex-nowrap gap-6 dark:text-white max-w-4xl font-mono">
  <div class="sm:border border-indigo-500 text-indigo-500 sm:h-full flex sm:items-center sm:justify-center sm:w-92 rounded aspect-square">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="rotate-45">
      <path d="M18 11V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2"/>
      <path d="M14 10V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2"/>
      <path d="M10 10.5V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v8"/>
      <path d="M18 8a2 2 0 1 1 4 0v6a8 8 0 0 1-8 8h-2c-2.8 0-4.5-.86-5.99-2.34l-3.6-3.6a2 2 0 0 1 2.83-2.82L7 15"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 items-start justify-end">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl border-b border-indigo-500 pb-2 font-semibold">
      Hello, I'm Charlie.
    </h2>
    <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      I'm a designer, developer, creative coder, and sometimes musician. I
      write about design and development.
      <a
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 font-semibold text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-400 dark:hover:text-indigo-300"
        href="/about"
      >
        <span>More about me</span> ❯
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
